1
00:00:15,060 --> 00:00:17,509
♪The world keeps changing♪

2
00:00:17,510 --> 00:00:19,979
♪A thousand years pass
in the blink of an eye♪

3
00:00:19,980 --> 00:00:22,159
♪Shoulder to shoulder♪

4
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:24,399
♪We stand above the world♪

5
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:26,590
♪Our identities switch♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:29,320
♪The world turns upside down♪

7
00:00:29,730 --> 00:00:31,729
♪Watch me♪

8
00:00:31,730 --> 00:00:35,319
♪Stir up a storm♪

9
00:00:35,320 --> 00:00:37,609
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

10
00:00:37,610 --> 00:00:40,059
♪Our blood is boiling♪

11
00:00:40,060 --> 00:00:45,289
♪The genius emperor plots
with brilliant strategy♪

12
00:00:45,290 --> 00:00:49,709
♪The slacker general
is unmatched in battle♪

13
00:00:49,710 --> 00:00:52,199
♪The business world is in turmoil♪

14
00:00:52,200 --> 00:00:54,749
♪The court is rife with intrigue♪

15
00:00:54,750 --> 00:00:59,169
♪We will conquer the world♪

16
00:00:59,170 --> 00:01:03,510
♪There's no escape for the traitors♪

17
00:01:05,080 --> 00:01:07,999
=No Way! My Bro is the Emperor=

18
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:11,160
=Episode 14=

19
00:01:12,100 --> 00:01:12,930
Your Majesty,

20
00:01:13,380 --> 00:01:14,700
what's bothering you?

21
00:01:15,020 --> 00:01:15,849
About my empress.

22
00:01:15,850 --> 00:01:17,080
- Your Majesty!
- Your Majesty!

23
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:18,840
(Honoring Learning and Confucianism)

24
00:01:19,020 --> 00:01:19,930
Out of the way.

25
00:01:20,130 --> 00:01:21,090
Wait for me.

26
00:01:21,620 --> 00:01:22,920
- Your Majesty.
- Your Majesty.

27
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:24,340
What is going on here?

28
00:01:27,300 --> 00:01:28,379
Your Majesty.

29
00:01:28,380 --> 00:01:30,049
- You can't always show Gu Nan such favor.
- Your Majesty.

30
00:01:30,050 --> 00:01:31,689
Today, you have to
spend some time with us.

31
00:01:31,690 --> 00:01:32,370
Your Majesty,

32
00:01:32,380 --> 00:01:33,969
I've just had a new silk dress made.

33
00:01:33,970 --> 00:01:34,849
You must see it.

34
00:01:34,850 --> 00:01:35,730
Your Majesty.

35
00:01:35,940 --> 00:01:36,730
Your Majesty.

36
00:01:37,460 --> 00:01:38,049
Gu Nan...

37
00:01:38,050 --> 00:01:38,700
Your Majesty,

38
00:01:39,020 --> 00:01:40,340
I've learned a new pastry recipe.

39
00:01:40,380 --> 00:01:41,980
You must come try it at my place.

40
00:01:42,100 --> 00:01:44,539
- Your Majesty.
- Your Majesty.

41
00:01:44,540 --> 00:01:45,340
Your Majesty.

42
00:01:45,380 --> 00:01:48,220
- Your Majesty.
- Your Majesty. Come to my palace.

43
00:01:50,330 --> 00:01:50,899
Your Majesty.

44
00:01:50,900 --> 00:01:51,860
Have a taste.

45
00:01:55,330 --> 00:01:56,530
What did you put

46
00:01:57,490 --> 00:01:58,539
in the soup?

47
00:01:58,540 --> 00:01:59,930
I added

48
00:01:59,940 --> 00:02:00,730
sea cucumber,

49
00:02:00,970 --> 00:02:01,849
abalone,

50
00:02:01,850 --> 00:02:02,730
and shark fin.

51
00:02:04,020 --> 00:02:04,570
I...

52
00:02:04,610 --> 00:02:06,220
I'm allergic to seafood.

53
00:02:07,410 --> 00:02:08,209
Your Majesty.

54
00:02:08,210 --> 00:02:08,810
Your Majesty.

55
00:02:08,860 --> 00:02:09,740
Your Majesty.

56
00:02:40,810 --> 00:02:47,620
The moon passes the red pavilion, through
carved windows, upon the sleepless.

57
00:02:54,300 --> 00:02:55,020
Your Majesty.

58
00:02:55,860 --> 00:02:57,740
You laughed, Your Majesty.

59
00:03:02,180 --> 00:03:03,370
Thank you, Your Majesty.

60
00:03:27,650 --> 00:03:29,900
I don't know what got into

61
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,840
Concubine Chun,
Noble Lady Li, and Consort Yu.

62
00:03:32,330 --> 00:03:33,580
They wouldn't leave me alone.

63
00:03:38,900 --> 00:03:40,220
They must've seen me

64
00:03:40,300 --> 00:03:42,250
promoted to Noble Consort

65
00:03:42,930 --> 00:03:44,780
and now want Your Majesty's favor too.

66
00:03:48,420 --> 00:03:49,410
How about

67
00:03:49,530 --> 00:03:51,899
I issue an edict
to disband the imperial harem?

68
00:03:51,900 --> 00:03:52,859
They can

69
00:03:52,860 --> 00:03:55,020
go home and find husbands of their own.

70
00:03:55,420 --> 00:03:56,180
No.

71
00:03:56,810 --> 00:03:58,580
They've done nothing wrong.

72
00:03:59,140 --> 00:04:00,740
If they're suddenly sent away,

73
00:04:00,860 --> 00:04:01,810
wouldn't they

74
00:04:01,860 --> 00:04:03,620
become the laughingstock?

75
00:04:04,420 --> 00:04:05,250
True.

76
00:04:06,020 --> 00:04:06,970
But this can't

77
00:04:07,490 --> 00:04:08,810
go on forever.

78
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:10,899
They've been confined
to the palace for so long.

79
00:04:10,900 --> 00:04:12,250
It's only natural

80
00:04:12,460 --> 00:04:14,060
they would feel lonely.

81
00:04:15,650 --> 00:04:18,059
They've money, property, and no debts.

82
00:04:18,060 --> 00:04:21,220
Which is to say
they've got too much free time.

83
00:04:21,900 --> 00:04:22,780
Bei,

84
00:04:22,850 --> 00:04:23,729
what brings you here?

85
00:04:23,730 --> 00:04:27,209
I was going to invite you two
to Xiaoyao Pavilion to try some new dishes.

86
00:04:27,210 --> 00:04:28,699
But I overheard someone

87
00:04:28,700 --> 00:04:30,850
competing with my sister
for Your Majesty's favor,

88
00:04:31,170 --> 00:04:32,490
so I came to see for myself.

89
00:04:33,140 --> 00:04:34,379
Stop teasing me.

90
00:04:34,380 --> 00:04:35,900
Help me think of something.

91
00:04:37,170 --> 00:04:39,139
People only have so much energy.

92
00:04:39,140 --> 00:04:41,059
If they've got that much spare time,

93
00:04:41,060 --> 00:04:44,410
all you have to do
is help them burn some of it off.

94
00:04:44,580 --> 00:04:45,380
Oh, right.

95
00:04:45,620 --> 00:04:47,220
Bring Xiao Ling along too.

96
00:04:47,260 --> 00:04:49,380
She looks like
she's got too much energy as well.

97
00:04:49,770 --> 00:04:50,700
Now

98
00:04:52,530 --> 00:04:54,290
here's what you're going to do.

99
00:05:09,632 --> 00:05:11,169
You Central Plains ladies

100
00:05:11,170 --> 00:05:12,940
are too delicate.

101
00:05:13,210 --> 00:05:13,900
Don't worry.

102
00:05:13,940 --> 00:05:15,089
Train with me,

103
00:05:15,090 --> 00:05:17,140
and you'll be tougher
than the men on the grasslands.

104
00:05:17,620 --> 00:05:18,380
Let's go.

105
00:05:49,530 --> 00:05:51,170
I can't do this anymore.

106
00:05:54,730 --> 00:05:55,940
I can't.

107
00:05:55,970 --> 00:05:56,900
I give up.

108
00:06:26,330 --> 00:06:27,240
What are you looking at?

109
00:06:27,850 --> 00:06:28,850
Get up and keep training.

110
00:06:29,330 --> 00:06:30,940
Monster!

111
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,320
- You...
- You...

112
00:06:34,940 --> 00:06:35,610
Ow!

113
00:06:38,260 --> 00:06:38,900
It hurts!

114
00:06:39,170 --> 00:06:40,380
I can't take this anymore.

115
00:06:40,700 --> 00:06:41,380
All right.

116
00:06:44,940 --> 00:06:45,610
How do you feel?

117
00:06:46,140 --> 00:06:47,290
Feeling any better

118
00:06:47,460 --> 00:06:48,780
after that stretch?

119
00:06:49,460 --> 00:06:50,850
I do feel a lot looser.

120
00:06:50,900 --> 00:06:51,970
That's amazing.

121
00:06:52,820 --> 00:06:54,139
I told them to work out.

122
00:06:54,140 --> 00:06:55,380
How did you end up joining them?

123
00:06:56,140 --> 00:06:58,340
It has been days
since I've had Qinghuan cakes.

124
00:07:01,770 --> 00:07:02,490
Your Majesty,

125
00:07:03,020 --> 00:07:04,220
you're the Emperor.

126
00:07:04,500 --> 00:07:06,820
Having a palace full of consorts
is only natural.

127
00:07:07,380 --> 00:07:08,900
I've never expected

128
00:07:09,020 --> 00:07:10,220
to have you all to myself.

129
00:07:11,210 --> 00:07:12,220
But

130
00:07:13,500 --> 00:07:15,380
why are you so good to me?

131
00:07:19,190 --> 00:07:20,840
Though the Weak Water
stretches three thousand li,

132
00:07:21,580 --> 00:07:22,970
I take but one ladle.

133
00:07:24,380 --> 00:07:25,900
To me,

134
00:07:26,730 --> 00:07:27,900
love is meant for

135
00:07:28,900 --> 00:07:30,170
one person

136
00:07:31,020 --> 00:07:31,970
for life.

137
00:07:39,090 --> 00:07:39,850
Right!

138
00:07:44,770 --> 00:07:45,380
I've prepared

139
00:07:46,090 --> 00:07:47,850
some gifts for you.

140
00:07:47,900 --> 00:07:49,090
See if you like any of these.

141
00:07:52,970 --> 00:07:53,970
You don't like them?

142
00:07:54,380 --> 00:07:55,020
I...

143
00:07:56,170 --> 00:07:57,259
I'm actually

144
00:07:57,260 --> 00:07:59,490
not very good at making girls happy.

145
00:08:00,090 --> 00:08:01,340
It was all Gu Bei.

146
00:08:01,410 --> 00:08:03,379
He said girls love getting gifts.

147
00:08:03,380 --> 00:08:04,820
I can't believe I listened to him.

148
00:08:05,330 --> 00:08:06,580
If you don't like them,

149
00:08:07,140 --> 00:08:08,460
we could

150
00:08:08,530 --> 00:08:09,580
go on a date.

151
00:08:11,260 --> 00:08:12,840
We could also go fishing
in the imperial garden.

152
00:08:12,900 --> 00:08:14,700
The peonies are in bloom.

153
00:08:14,850 --> 00:08:15,610
We...

154
00:09:05,500 --> 00:09:06,890
Your Majesty, I have a memorial.

155
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:08,490
Your Majesty has long
ascended the throne,

156
00:09:08,500 --> 00:09:10,049
yet the position of Empress
remains vacant.

157
00:09:10,050 --> 00:09:11,099
I humbly ask Your Majesty

158
00:09:11,100 --> 00:09:12,540
to appoint an Empress soon

159
00:09:12,650 --> 00:09:13,890
to reassure the people.

160
00:09:14,100 --> 00:09:15,010
I think

161
00:09:15,500 --> 00:09:17,090
you make a good point.

162
00:09:17,340 --> 00:09:18,339
Consort Nan

163
00:09:18,340 --> 00:09:19,730
holds a special place in my heart.

164
00:09:20,050 --> 00:09:21,490
I intend to make her Empress.

165
00:09:22,050 --> 00:09:23,460
What do you all think?

166
00:09:30,380 --> 00:09:31,700
Your Majesty,

167
00:09:31,900 --> 00:09:32,689
I don't think

168
00:09:32,690 --> 00:09:34,220
it's a good idea.

169
00:09:38,280 --> 00:09:40,119
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

170
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:42,519
♪Our spirit soars to the skies♪

171
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:47,959
♪The brainy emperor plots the strategy♪

172
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:52,319
♪The slacker general leads the charge♪

173
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:54,719
♪Swords clash and warhorses thunder♪

174
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:57,279
♪Let the history judge our deeds♪

175
00:09:57,280 --> 00:10:02,959
♪Our brotherhood is priceless♪

176
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:08,520
♪Peace across the land, carefree at last♪

177
00:10:12,800 --> 00:10:14,840
♪Funny moments never stop♪

178
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:17,680
♪Silly blunders never cease♪

179
00:10:17,880 --> 00:10:22,039
♪Yet through every up and down♪

180
00:10:22,040 --> 00:10:24,000
♪We create miracles♪

181
00:10:24,320 --> 00:10:26,760
♪From naive youths♪

182
00:10:27,040 --> 00:10:29,519
♪To legendary heroes♪

183
00:10:29,520 --> 00:10:31,439
♪This journey♪

184
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:35,479
♪Is one we'll be proud of♪

185
00:10:35,480 --> 00:10:38,000
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

186
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:43,360
♪Let's create♪

187
00:10:45,400 --> 00:10:53,320
♪A legend of our own♪

